title: SSX On Tour HD PC Remaster - Install and Play.exe
description:
This is an installation pack for one of my favorite games of all time SSX On Tour.  This is the Gamecube version of the game that runs in a special Dolphin configuration.  All the settings have been configured for maximimum compatibility, performance, and graphics.  

Just run the installer and launch the game just like any other PC game.  You will not have to see or mess with Dolphin
